{"tid":1153873,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍天瑞邨男子危企　警趕抵時墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-05-14T02:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T03:23:39.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3a70a100997ddf948003dcdd1ff884278dd8bf","tid":1153873,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"天水圍天瑞邨瑞財樓，今早（14日）8時，一名男子報案，指女友的20餘歲兄長在走廊危站欄河外，企圖跳樓尋死。警方趕至時，再接獲大廈保安員報案，指危企事主已墮下，飛跌落平台重傷。救護員到場救援，證實男子已傷重死亡，警方正調查男子的尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=7ca6d32a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190514/mobile/bkn-20190514085447270-0514_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190514%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190514085447270-0514_00822_001.html&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=5b01a2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190514/mobile/bkn-20190514085447270-0514_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4b4bbc00186a86b11b5a2cbb8d8a55e0fa4aebeb","tid":1153873,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/hTCptUCaVTgzYqOBcT/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FhTCptUCaVTgzYqOBcT%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c8d0b992&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9824e69a92f1fe42f5b869000e59ad9a7713c12","tid":1153873,"uid":7452,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:27:44.000Z","m